{"tid":2459690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得世界末日都唔錯","createTime":"2021-03-24T10:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T08:46:23.000Z","uid":109021,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"15062622affe8745d974c9811624cb5d6444d026","tid":2459690,"uid":109021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T10:26:36.000Z","msg":"感覺好似個世界愈嚟愈差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且自己都無乜特別留戀，再繼續落去都唔會有咩改善咁<br />\n如果世界末日就可以停留係比較美好嘅一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445aaaa351048892cdd9568413c89e0740153289","tid":2459690,"uid":109021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818e6c0db08abb5853f73bbf5b08fa36b05a5487","tid":2459690,"uid":109021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1f7e8502e31b5de8e7beb1d68812d62b5717d2","tid":2459690,"uid":109021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T10:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ed71ac99c304a5c85ac712ee30d607135ce1ae1","tid":2459690,"uid":337336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"攬炒好，攬炒妙，攬炒好到不得了"},{"pid":"1f93437c62ef5844f4e7ecdbd0122a7f4f4e9036","tid":2459690,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"由細到大都想個世界快啲結束"},{"pid":"06626e1553415e57d07fbb7babdcbec0f272d8cc","tid":2459690,"uid":41174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"爆炸左佢咪算"},{"pid":"badae501d3cd2be4d21614e5a9a4bae6038879cb","tid":2459690,"uid":109021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1